        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What he doesn’t mention is any of the tips, tricks, hacks, or shortcuts that many companies and people invest in all the time, to short-circuit their success (if only until their competition catches up, and applies the same tactic).",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That’s probably because once those techniques are ubiquitous - as in:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "used by everyone",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "- they’re no longer a competitive advantage. They’re just something that everyone (in an industry) does because they think it’s going to help them succeed.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "As Morgan points out, “everything else - intelligence, design, insight – gets smashed to pieces by competitors who are almost certainly as smart as you” —because they are. Knowledge has its limits.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The best way to gain a competitive advantage is to invest in things your competitors",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "aren’t",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "willing to invest in. Things that are challenging and difficult, and that take time to pay off.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Caring more. Failing faster. Learning all that you can.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Doing your best possible work instead of settling for the best you can do.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
